From cou.: 10 On the other hand, NHDF cells were seeded in 6-well culture dishes at 100000 cells per well and incubated for 24 h at 37 °C and 5% CO2. Culture medium was removed, replaced with lentiviral particles, and incubated for 48 h at 37 °C and 5% CO2. After the removal of lentiviral particles, fresh medium was added and the cultures were examined for GFP expression by using fluorescence microscopy. The expression of GFP could be visually detected 24 h after virus treatment. NHDF cells were subsequently analyzed using the fluorescence activated cell sorting (FACS) method to physically isolate only NHDF-GFP clones.
From Soup: 10 On the other hand, NHDF cells were seeded in 6-well culture dishes at 100 000 cells per well and incubated for 24 h at 37 °C and 5% CO 2 . Culture medium was removed, replaced with lentiviral particles, and incubated for 48 h at 37 °C and 5% CO 2 . After the removal of lentiviral particles, fresh medium was added and the cultures were examined for GFP expression by using fluorescence microscopy. The expression of GFP could be visually detected 24 h after virus treatment. NHDF cells were subsequently analyzed using the fluorescence activated cell sorting (FACS) method to physically isolate only NHDF-GFP clones.
